text: Songs from the West Coast is the 26th studio album by Elton John and was released on 1 October 2001. It went to top 20 in Australia, Austria, Canada, Denmark, France, Germany, Italy, the Netherlands, Norway, Poland, Sweden, Switzerland, the United Kingdom and the United States. It was nominated for an Grammy Award in 2002. == Track listing == All songs written by Elton John and Bernie Taupin. Category:2001 albums Category:Elton John albums
title: Songs from the West Coast
